{"tid":1779070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲記唔記得呢位手足 佢聽日要上庭啦","createTime":"2019-12-11T12:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T08:18:29.000Z","uid":225973,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"1b81d72a2c38494cc83836eb84df920b0be2cef0","tid":1779070,"uid":225973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"［公投］條友噴鐘樓割唔割席<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434109</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思借朋友ac一用 呢位手足係我朋友 <br />\n唔知大家仲記唔記得佢 嗰陣新聞一出 引起過好大迴響 <br />\n當時有啲人話佢on9 無腦 亦有啲人表示核爆都唔割<br />\n而依家佢被控<span style=\"color: red;\"> 刑毁 嚴重傷人 </span> 聽日判刑 <br />\n佢自己同律師都覺得坐硬 打定輸數要入去坐 <br />\n將會係呢場運動成為第二個判監既手足 <br />\n希望大家聽日得閒 幫幫手去聲援吓集吓氣 手足唔係condom  <br />\n感激大家！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">12/12 早上九點十五分 九龍城法院 一號庭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 光復香港 時代革命 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 五大訴求 缺一不可 </span>"},{"pid":"b2e811d8ad82ad4c15aae7804c6962735248ced0","tid":1779070,"uid":225973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:18:42.000Z","msg":"推到有人睇"},{"pid":"40e4e0b5c2a0213e2bd9c23876e0879174139727","tid":1779070,"uid":66889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9b1e974e3051241ecf15367fb3a9df1bc93483","tid":1779070,"uid":121260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c4af061dbfa792ab6cb0769135fd79f941cee4","tid":1779070,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b81d72a2c38494cc83836eb84df920b0be2cef0","tid":1779070,"uid":225973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"［公投］